node.title: Man facing murder charge over Swanson man's death
node.description: Police have upgraded charges against a 31-year-old man, in relation to a death in west Aucklander over the weekend.
node.content:
["Police have upgraded charges against a 31 year old man, in relation to a death in west Aucklander over the weekend.", "", "
\nPhoto: RNZ / Patrice Allen\n
", "David Keith Yates, 65, was found dead at a house on Candia Road in Swanson on Saturday morning.", "A man charged with assault, now faces a murder charge.", "He is due to appear in the Waitakere District Court tomorrow.", "The police are not seeking anyone else in connection with Yates' death."]
